scene.message:
Yog-Sothoth Jr.:{nl}
Gck, gck, gck...{nl}
You who have struck me down...{waitkey}{clearbox}My master, too, shall find{nl}
you to her liking.{nl}
Go on, proceed...{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: Aww, so that monster{nl}
got beaten, huh.{waitkey}{clearbox}Losing to people like{nl}
these - how stupid~!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Aki...chan!{nl}
You've come to pull{nl}
something again, haven't you!{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: Beyond here is Aki's{nl}
house. Come in, and I'll{nl}
never let you back outside!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Say what you like,{nl}
but we're coming in.{waitkey}{clearbox}We have to defeat{nl}
Kandori.{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: ...{wait_fr:48}I won't ever{nl}
let you do that!{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you're in Aki's house,{nl}
I'll lock you up for good!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: You dummy.{nl}
Like I'd fall for the same{nl}
trick twice!{waitkey}{clearbox}Now then, be a good girl,{nl}
or I'll really have to{nl}
punish you, got it?{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: Aki's not stupid!{nl}
As proof, I thought up{nl}
something really fun!{waitkey}{clearbox}...Your next opponent{nl}
is a cuuute little girl.{nl}
Look forward to it!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: That Aki-chan{nl}
what a cheeky kid she is.{waitkey}{clearbox}This time I'll catch her{nl}
and scold her for sure!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: That cute little girl{nl}
she mentioned... she meant{nl}
Chisato, didn't she...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: There's something{nl}
that's been bothering me...{waitkey}{clearbox}...No, I've no proof.{nl}
It's surely just a{nl}
mistake on my part.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That demon here{nl}
spoke of a 'master.'{nl}
Did it mean Aki?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: All right, let's get{nl}
outside and hunt down{nl}
that Kandori!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Here we are still{nl}
wandering around a place{nl}
like this.{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, at this rate, can we{nl}
really save Sonomura?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: About that demon that{nl}
was here...{waitkey}{clearbox}It almost felt as though{nl}
it were testing our skill.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Phew!{nl}
I'm just glad that{nl}
monster is gone!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ugh!{nl}
Ayase is never fighting{nl}
something like that again!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: The town suddenly{nl}
going strange, demons{nl}
starting to appear...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
What happened to this town?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: You're not taking{nl}
that brat's words{nl}
seriously, are you?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: There's something I{nl}
absolutely have to make{nl}
Kandori answer for...{waitkey}{ret}
